  "text": "Some studies have suggested that drugs that inhibit NF-κB combined with GEM can improve the therapeutic effects of GEM on pancreatic and gallbladder cancers. effects on pancreatic cancer cells; [CITATION_1] thus, NF-κB may be a promising target for reducing MRD.",
